    "He also heard lectures by the cultural sociologist and art writer Georg Simmel (1858-1918), the philosopher Moritz Lazarus (1824-1903), the historian Heinrich von Treitschke (1834-1896) and the social economist Adolf Wagner (1835-1917).": [
