    "In 1902 he was commissioned to write on French Impressionism by the art historian <a href=\"/mutherr\">Richard Muther</a> for Muther's pocket-sized surveys of art, the <em>Klassische Illustratoren</em> series and the <em>Sammlung illustrierter Monographien</em>.": [
