    "The first volume was <em>Edouard Manet und sein Kreis</em>.": [],
    "His gallery closed in 1903 and he returned to Berlin to write his ground-breaking history of modern art, <em>Die Entwicklungsgeschichte der modernen Kunst</em> (The Developmental History of Modern Art).": [
