    "Together with the art historian <a href=\"/hausensteinw\">Wilhelm Hausenstein</a>, he edited the art-history yearbook, <em>Ganymede</em>, beginning in 1919.": [],
    "He moved to Berlin in 1921, occupying a house designed by architect and architectural historian <a href=\"/muthesiush\">Hermann Muthesius</a>.": [],
